a" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>之后，卡古拉·毛拉（Kagura Maura</strong></a> ）的合作“ Robel no Tomea”上传了“同一故事”封面。唱着潮湿信任的歌曲具有很高的歌唱能力的两个人正在仔细唱歌，并使其变得美丽。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-jpg.webp 1254w" width="1024" height="572" /></a></p><p>最初，“ Robel Timea”始于多次合作的惩罚游戏，但是当您重复数字时，您可以在互相战斗时一起笑，您可以一起笑。这是一种流行的组合，已经开始像即使在原始数量之后，也一直在协作。歌曲也反映了娱乐性的独特味道，只能给两个具有独特距离感的人，这也反映在歌曲中。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[#robelnaitomea]我们在2024年问候[晚上Robel/Kagura Mea]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wS28GE_Pvw0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>尽管即使您独自听这首歌也可以享受高质量，但如果您对通常的“ Robel Nomi Time”有所了解，这将更加愉快。</p><p>单击此处以获取过去的推荐文章：<br /><a href="https://www.moguravr.com/category/vtuber-weekly-infomation/">必看！推荐本周的Vtuber</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-weekly-23-1-21/">这段视频的帖子很棒！推荐本周的VTUBER视频（〜1月19日）</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
